  26:sbc_comms.c   **** // Copied for Pi software codebase
  27:sbc_comms.c   **** // We use a Cyclic Redundancy Check (CRC).
  28:sbc_comms.c   **** // The CRC takes the whole message as one binary number, divides it by 0x07
ARM GAS  C:\Users\yoons\AppData\Local\Temp\ccqalARB.s 			page 8


